    "content_list_QeNEja": {
      "type": "content-list",
      "blocks": {
        "image_q3WXTc": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/OOAKV012Front.jpg",
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underCenter",
            "subheading": "<p>MOZAMBIQUE RUBY</p>",
            "title": "<p>'As Long As There Is Love' Solitaire</p>",
            "description": "<p>Ruby, with its rich red hue, has long been a totem of love, passion, and power. Known as the ‘king of gemstones,’ it has been treasured across cultures for its deep, fiery colour, often associated with the heart. </p><p>In ancient times, rubies were believed to protect warriors in battle and ward off evil. But they also illustrated vitality and life force, making them popular in romantic jewellery as tokens of intense love and commitment. </p><p>Wrapping wire work, and small metal details paired with our Vieira Setting, a Natalie Marie Jewellery take on a vintage scalloped setting, this piece encourages us to think of all the elements involved in love, and act as a reminder of their importance as a whole.</p>",
            "description_mobile": "<p>Ruby, with its rich red hue, has long been a totem of love, passion, and power. Known as the ‘king of gemstones,’ it has been treasured across cultures for its deep, fiery colour, often associated with the heart. </p><p>In ancient times, rubies were believed to protect warriors in battle and ward off evil. But they also illustrated vitality and life force, making them popular in romantic jewellery as tokens of intense love and commitment. </p><p>Wrapping wire work, and small metal details paired with our Vieira Setting, a Natalie Marie Jewellery take on a vintage scalloped setting, this piece encourages us to think of all the elements involved in love, and act as a reminder of their importance as a whole.</p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
            "button_1_metaobject": "",
            "button_1_text": "EXPLORE NOW",
            "button_1_link": "shopify://products/as-long-as-there-is-love-solitaire-ruby",
            "button_2_metaobject": "",
            "button_2_text": "",
            "button_2_link": "",
            "button_3_metaobject": "",
            "button_3_text": "",
            "button_3_link": "",
